    "description": "《刀剑竞技场》是一款俯视角回合制策略游戏。玩家将操控一把枪在一众冷兵器的包围中突围！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>操作易上手，策略难精通</strong></h2>游戏的按键不多，用鼠标瞄准4个方向，左键按下即可发射。由于后坐力的影响，会同时向后退。也就是一个按键同时实现了攻击和移动。所以玩家每次的行为都需要三思而行，考虑每次射击将带来的一系列连锁反应。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169910/extras/448f71c5f198549948b98fcd7d1e78fe.poster.avif?t=1732637928\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169910/extras/448f71c5f198549948b98fcd7d1e78fe.webm?t=1732637928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169910/extras/448f71c5f198549948b98fcd7d1e78fe.mp4?t=1732637928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>敌人意图透明，击杀更具策略性</strong></h2>观察、理解、识破敌人的行为模式，通过合理的走位躲避危险，击杀敌人<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169910/extras/c0998defb5fb81de78b3fa9637a0e0b8.poster.avif?t=1732637928\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169910/extras/c0998defb5fb81de78b3fa9637a0e0b8.webm?t=1732637928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169910/extras/c0998defb5fb81de78b3fa9637a0e0b8.mp4?t=1732637928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>肉鸽升级，让玩法更具深度</strong></h2>玩家每通过一关，就可以在随机的三项能力中选择一项进行升级，穿透、自动瞄准、击退、爆炸等。强大也伴随着不小的风险，例如贴脸的爆炸会伤害到自己。自动瞄准，有时并不会优先攻击你想要的目标。如何合理地构筑自己的能力，探索不同的武器和能力之间的联动，也成为“必修课”之一！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169910/extras/e0fba972e1495892edc9c5c413d835e3.poster.avif?t=1732637928\" width=600 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169910/extras/e0fba972e1495892edc9c5c413d835e3.webm?t=1732637928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169910/extras/e0fba972e1495892edc9c5c413d835e3.mp4?t=1732637928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
